snippet.title: Aesop Rock - Long Legged Larry - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD THE GAME: https://AesopRock.com/Game
LISTEN / BUY "LONG LEGGED LARRY": https://rse.lnk.to/LLL
SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE: https://bit.ly/RhymesayersYT 

Aesop Rock's beloved tale of Long Legged Larry continues in this arcade style platformer. Play as a heroic frog named Larry who uses his extraordinary hopping skills to save a few newfound friends in need. This game offers two difficulty levels to choose from and many challenges to overcome as you valiantly hop your way through multiple levels of danger. Download free today to help Larry save the day!
